                config_layer {
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------
// | PSCRN | F1 | F2  | F3  | F4  | BTCLR|                  | BTCAL|  HOME |  UP  |  END  |VOL+  |SLEEP  |
// |       | F5 | F6  | F7  | F8  | BT0  |                  | BT1  |  LEFT | DOWN | RIGHT |VOL-  | OFF   |
// |       | F9 | F10 | F11 | F12 | BTX0 |                  | BTX1 |  PGUP | END  | PGDN  |MUTE  | PLAY  |
